{"tid":467851,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［解畫］直認同醫生男友分手 陳嘉倩同凸肚男了解中","createTime":"2017-11-14T01:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T14:35:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dd55f605ad9dbb491262d6c8b9dd9b7ee63c7b13","tid":467851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/091612_ae59a4676f2206a2be9941a96911fc36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F091612_ae59a4676f2206a2be9941a96911fc36.jpg&h=626ffa4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/091612_d82f5be14715387d0dadc42cdb22390a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F091612_d82f5be14715387d0dadc42cdb22390a.jpg&h=fe77ae5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳嘉倩喺離開無綫之後，第一次去拍廣告，仲做埋代言人，喺廣告入面有好多唔同嘅造型，有個運動造型同埋主播嘅造型。陳嘉倩就話拍廣告同做主播好唔同，一日要拍十幾個鐘，都係個新嘗試，不過佢就覺得唔係好辛苦，都拍得好順，講到收入係咪好過做主播，佢就話：「咁冇得比嘅。」問到會唔會都想做幕前拍下電視劇咁，陳嘉倩就話自己係讀緊書，如果有時間的話都唔會抗拒，不過暫時就冇人搵佢。<br />\n<br />\n早前陳嘉倩就被影到同一個凸肚男人一齊拍拖，但外界有傳呢位凸肚男有個女友、而陳嘉倩本身就有一個醫生男友，今日講到佢嘅感情生活多姿多彩，佢就話：「從來都冇話多姿多彩，上次影到嗰位係發展中、了解中。」至於係唔係有另一位男友，佢就話：「其實係之前嘅事，都已經分咗手，我都唔知點解會有啲咁嘅傳聞，不過每個人都有以前嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\n又講到凸肚男友本身有位女友，陳嘉倩就話：「 唔會有啦，我哋了解中，都係正式交往。」又有網民指陳嘉倩收兵，佢就話：「我冇睇到喎，從來都冇話諗過，冇當過人係兵，正常交朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n更多娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyent&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=39f68886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyent</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171113/57455199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57455199&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fe6cd154\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57455199&h=f8b36d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171113/57455199</a><br />\n<br />\n點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755fa540a33684548cedb540b8b8d138f444e9c9","tid":467851,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地扑野帶唔帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85231587a0c88332ce9bd572f0cdb49c94cc3095","tid":467851,"uid":64948,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:19:44.000Z","msg":"個死肥仔都唔知前世做過咩好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能交個老母出來比日本仔強姦換來全家人兩餐溫飽<br />\n<br />\n先得來溝到個咁正既囡囡"},{"pid":"c6ccc4e7dc0c07fa54d02498b8541ec3d2f3d38b","tid":467851,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"個樣同做主播嗰陣差咁遠嘅，同埋睇下半身啲肉鬆到好似生完仔嘅師奶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f26f46b4b9135eabde25b01a21a6c9732d612a","tid":467851,"uid":86029,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個死肥仔都唔知前世做過咩好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能交個老母出來比日本仔強姦換來全家人兩餐溫飽<br />\n<br />\n先得來溝到個咁正既囡囡</blockquote><br />\n你唔好咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1d1a7d388d16a2d09d1362da81cc3e29a4545b","tid":467851,"uid":117837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:44:31.000Z","msg":"了解到帶埋返上屋企又撩又解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aa1b4856848da09d742d0dd9b948cda806dddd","tid":467851,"uid":51041,"like":0,"disli